Maker: William "^taskY" Graham.

This was not made by me, it was made by my friend taskY. 
He never released it, and I liked it alot so I decided to fix up what he didn't finish and release it.

De_saint.
Terrorists start outside, counter-terrorists start inside.
2 bombsites, many routes to each site.

This map isn't final IMO, but I'm releasing it that way.
Suggestions will be ignored.

Have fun.
